# Vector Multiplier

## Overview
Performs element-wise multiplication between two vectors.

## Board
Arty A7 (Artix-7)

## Tools
- Verilog
- Xilinx Vivado

## Description
Each element of one vector is multiplied with the corresponding element of another vector to produce an output vector.

## Inputs
- Vector A
- Vector B

## Outputs
- Resulting vector

## Notes
Focuses on handling multiple data elements and parallel operations in Verilog.
